title: John Boehner cancels 'Tonight Show' appearance at last minute
text:
John Boehner cancels 'Tonight Show' a... John Boehner cancels 'Tonight Show' appearance at last minute 36 min ago Read more: Los Angeles Times 
Maybe he wasn't ready to slow-jam the news? John A. Boehner has pulled out of a scheduled appearance on "The Tonight Show." The Republican speaker of the House, who announced his stunning decision to resign from Congress two weeks ago, had been slated to visit the NBC talk show Thursday night, but will not be appearing, NBC confirmed to the Times.
